text: Filip Dvořák (born December 2, 1976) is a Czech former professional ice hockey player who played 26 games in the Czech Extraliga over two seasons. Dvořák made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Olomouc during the 1995-96 Czech Extraliga season. ==External links== * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:HC Olomouc players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards
